Class Table

java.lang.Object
Table
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Table extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a table in the restaurant. There are a total of 20 tables, 4 tables for each table capacity of 2,4,6,8, and 10. For each table capacity, there are 2 smoking and 2 non‐smoking tables.
